metadata.name: Bad Days #1/20
metadata.description:
Some illustrations that are unfinished, or finished but unsatisfactory. Frustrations on technique, art direction, or composition are part of an artist's progress. How many more works are actually hidden from public's eyes? 
When people say "you're talented" or "you make it look so easy", these are the example of the bad days artwork that accompanies every artists for as long as they try to improve.
